==研究==
在過去的30年中，歐文發表了300多篇經過[[同行評審|同行評審]]的[[科學論文|科學論文]]，以及40多個章節和書籍。<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.owenlab.uwo.ca/publications/index.html|title = Publications - Owen Lab|website = Western University|access-date = 13 April 2016|archive-date = 2018-09-24|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180924235725/http://www.owenlab.uwo.ca/publications/index.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>他的成果出現在許多世界上最負盛名的[[科學期刊|科學]]和[[醫學期刊|醫學期刊]]上，包括《[[科學_(期刊)|科學]]》、《[[自然_(期刊)|自然]]》、《[[柳葉刀|柳葉刀]]》和《[[新英格蘭醫學雜誌|新英格蘭醫學雜誌]]》。他的H指數（[[Google學術搜索|Google學術搜索]]）目前為110。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://scholar.google.ca/citations?user=wPFn1OsAAAAJ&hl=en|title=Google Scholar - Adrian Owen|last=|first=|date=29 April 2020|website=|url-status=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180824002244/https://scholar.google.ca/citations?user=wPFn1OsAAAAJ&hl=en|archive-date=2018-08-24|access-date=}}</ref>

他關於[[額葉|額葉]]或[[顳葉|顳葉]]切除患者的早期出版物<ref name="autogenerated632">{{cite journal |last1=Owen |first1=Adrian M |last2=Coleman |first2=Martin R |title=Functional MRI in disorders of consciousness: advantages and limitations |journal=Current Opinion in Neurology |volume=20 |issue=6 |pages=632–7 |year=2007 |pmid=17992081 |doi=10.1097/WCO.0b013e3282f15669}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Owen |first1=A |last2=Downes |first2=JJ |last3=Sahakian |first3=BJ |last4=Polkey |first4=CE |last5=Robbins |first5=TW |title=Planning and spatial working memory following frontal lobe lesions in man |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_neuropsychologia_1990_28_10/page/1021 |journal=Neuropsychologia |volume=28 |issue=10 |pages=1021–34 |year=1990 |pmid=2267054 |doi=10.1016/0028-3932(90)90137-D}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Owen |first1=A |last2=Roberts |first2=AC |last3=Polkey |first3=CE |last4=Sahakian |first4=BJ |last5=Robbins |first5=TW |title=Extra-dimensional versus intra-dimensional set shifting performance following frontal lobe excisions, temporal lobe excisions or amygdalo-hippocampectomy in man |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_neuropsychologia_1991_29_10/page/993 |journal=Neuropsychologia |volume=29 |issue=10 |pages=993–1006 |year=1991 |pmid=1762678 |doi=10.1016/0028-3932(91)90063-E}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Owen |first1=A. M. |last2=James |first2=M. |last3=Leigh |first3=P. N. |last4=Summers |first4=B. A. |last5=Marsden |first5=C. D. |last6=Quinn |first6=N. P. |last7=Lange |first7=K. W. |last8=Robbins |first8=T. W. |title=Fronto-Striatal Cognitive Deficits at Different Stages of Parkinson's Disease |journal=Brain |volume=115 |issue=6 |pages=1727–51 |year=1992 |pmid=1486458 |doi=10.1093/brain/115.6.1727 |url=https://epub.uni-regensburg.de/25426/1/langekw8.pdf |access-date=2020-11-25 |archive-date=2017-08-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170814083042/https://epub.uni-regensburg.de/25426/1/langekw8.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Owen |first1=A |last2=Sahakian |first2=BJ |last3=Semple |first3=J |last4=Polkey |first4=CE |last5=Robbins |first5=TW |title=Visuo-spatial short-term recognition memory and learning after temporal lobe excisions, frontal lobe excisions or amygdalo-hippocampectomy in man |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_neuropsychologia_1995-01_33_1/page/n4 |journal=Neuropsychologia |volume=33 |issue=1 |pages=1–24 |year=1995 |pmid=7731533 |doi=10.1016/0028-3932(94)00098-A}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Owen |first1=Adrian M. |last2=Morris |first2=Robin G. |last3=Sahakian |first3=Barbara J. |last4=Polkey |first4=Charles E. |last5=Robbins |first5=Trevor W. |title=Double dissociations of memory and executive functions in working memory tasks following frontal lobe excisions, temporal lobe excisions or amygdalo-hippocampectomy in man |journal=Brain |volume=119 |issue=5 |pages=1597–615 |year=1996 |pmid=8931583 |doi=10.1093/brain/119.5.1597|doi-access=free }}</ref>開創了基於電腦觸控屏幕的認知測試在[[神經心理學|神經心理學]]領域的應用。在過去的30年中，這些測試已用於[[帕金森氏症|帕金森氏症]]、[[阿茲海默症|阿茲海默症]]、[[亨廷頓氏舞蹈症|亨廷頓氏舞蹈症]]、[[抑鬱症|抑鬱症]]、[[精神分裂症|精神分裂症]]、[[自閉症|自閉症]]、[[強迫症|強迫症]]和[[多動症|多動症]]等600多項已發表的研究中。

他與Michael Petrides進行的關於[[工作記憶|工作記憶]]的博士後研究（[[PNAS|PNAS]]、[[大腦皮質|大腦皮質]]、[[認知神經科學|認知神經科學]]雜誌和[[大腦|大腦]]等）有助於駁斥當時由Patricia Goldman-Rakic等人提出的外側[[額葉|額葉]]組織的主流觀點， 並且在這種情況下仍被廣泛引用。

他在1996年發表的有關人類額葉內工作記憶過程組織的論文，仍然是科學雜誌《[[大腦皮質_(期刊)|大腦皮質]]》中被引用次數最多的文章之一。<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Owen |first1=Adrian M. |last2=Evans |first2=Alan C. |last3=Petrides |first3=Michael |title=Evidence for a Two-Stage Model of Spatial Working Memory Processing within the Lateral Frontal Cortex: A Positron Emission Tomography Study |journal=Cerebral Cortex |volume=6 |issue=1 |pages=31–8 |year=1996 |pmid=8670636 |doi=10.1093/cercor/6.1.31|doi-access=free }}</ref>

他在2006年發表在《科學》期刊上的論文<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Owen |first1=Adrian M. |last2=Coleman |first2=Martin R. |title=Detecting Awareness in the Vegetative State |journal=Annals of the New York Academy of Sciences |volume=1129 |issue=1 |pages=130–8 |year=2008 |pmid=18591475 |doi=10.1196/annals.1417.018 |bibcode=2008NYASA1129..130O |url=https://orbi.uliege.be/bitstream/2268/130307/1/VS_science2006.pdf |access-date=2020-11-25 |archive-date=2022-06-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220605173742/https://orbi.uliege.be//bitstream/2268/130307/1/VS_science2006.pdf }}</ref>首次證明，功能神經影像學可用於檢測無法產生任何公認的行為反應且似乎處於[[持續性植物狀態|持續性植物狀態]]的患者的意識。這一具有里程碑意義的發現對臨床護理、診斷、醫學倫理和醫學/法律決策（與嚴重腦損傷後生命的延長有關）具有影響。<ref name="autogenerated632"/><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Fins |first1=JJ |last2=Schiff |first2=ND |title=Shades of Gray: New Insights into the Vegetative State. |journal=[[Hastings_Center_Report|Hastings Center Report]] |volume=36 |issue=6 |pages=8|year=2006 |doi=10.1353/hcr.2006.0094|pmid=17278863 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Owen |first1=Adrian M. |last2=Coleman |first2=Martin R. |title=Functional neuroimaging of the vegetative state |journal=Nature Reviews Neuroscience |volume=9 |issue=3 |pages=235–43 |year=2008 |pmid=18285801 |doi=10.1038/nrn2330}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Owen |first1=AM |last2=Coleman |first2=MR |title=Using neuroimaging to detect awareness in disorders of consciousness |journal=Functional Neurology |volume=23 |issue=4 |pages=189–94 |year=2008 |pmid=19331781 |url=http://www.functionalneurology.it/index.php?PAGE=article&ID=3329 |access-date=2020-11-25 |archive-date=2012-03-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120317044741/http://www.functionalneurology.it/index.php?PAGE=article&ID=3329 |dead-url=no }}</ref>在2010年《新英格蘭醫學雜誌》的後續論文中，<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Monti |first1=Martin M. |last2=Vanhaudenhuyse |first2=Audrey |last3=Coleman |first3=Martin R. |last4=Boly |first4=Melanie |last5=Pickard |first5=John D. |last6=Tshibanda |first6=Luaba |last7=Owen |first7=Adrian M. |last8=Laureys |first8=Steven |s2cid=13358991 |title=Willful Modulation of Brain Activity in Disorders of Consciousness |journal=New England Journal of Medicine |volume=362 |issue=7 |pages=579–89 |year=2010 |pmid=20130250 |doi=10.1056/NEJMoa0905370}}</ref>歐文和他的團隊使用了類似的方法，利用[[功能性磁振造影|功能性磁振造影]]偵測大腦活動的改變來使一個被認為處於持續性植物狀態超過5年的人能回答“是”和“否”的問題。<ref>Boseleys, S [https://www.theguardian.com/science/2010/feb/03/vegetative-state-patient-communication "Think tennis for yes, home for no: how doctors helped man in vegetative state"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.theguardian.com/science/2010/feb/03/vegetative-state-patient-communication |date=20210310000955 }} The Guardian, 3 February 2010.</ref>

這項研究引起了世界媒體的國際關注。全世界數百家報紙都報導過(包括《[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]》和其他大報)，並已在電視(如[[BBC|BBC]]、[[CNN|CNN]])、電台、被廣泛討論。迄今為止，這一發現已在6檔[[電視紀錄片|電視紀錄片]]中佔據重要地位，其中包括[[60分鐘|60分鐘]]、英國廣播公司全景報導、由內而外、和加拿大廣播公司國家。

==書籍==
2017年6月，歐文發表了一本[[科普|科普]]書籍《困在大腦裡的人：一位神經科學家探索生與死的界線》 ，講述了他20年的探索故事，以表明有些患者被認為是[[植物人|植物人]]的患者實際上是有意識的，但卻無法向外界表明。該書被《星期日泰晤士報》評為“年度最佳圖書” ，並被《泰晤士報》評為“本週最佳圖書”，在《紐約客》榜單“我們今年夏天讀什麼書”上名列其中，並獲得4.9分。 亞馬遜5星。該書已被翻譯成多種語言，包括意大利文、法文、俄文、德文、中文、日文、捷克文和波蘭文。

